title: Episode Seven: John Ross Bowie - Weekend Warriors
description:
Happy Holidays Psych-O's! This week, we got a special visit from our good friend John Ross Bowie, aka the dorky dentist with the hot wife in Season One, Episode 6 Weekend Warriors. He talks about his time on Psych, gives secret insider information about the episode, and how he had a connection to Psych even before this episode was shot!
